article_title: Learn about health insurance, scam awareness at Bayliss Public Library
article_text:
Learn about health insurance, scam awareness at Bayliss Public Library

Posted May. 14, 2016 at 10:32 AM



Sault Ste. Marie

article_metadata.description:
In an effort to help educate Michigan consumers on health insurance and scam awareness, the Michigan Department of Insurance and Financial Services (DIFS) will be hosting a free presentation at the Bayliss Public Library on Wednesday, May 18, from 2-4:30 p.m.
There will be two presentations (resource materials and tips provided):
